            <p>School Man reserves the right to update or change the privacy policy at any time and you should check this privacy policy periodically. Your continued use of the service after School Man posts any modifications to the privacy policy on this page will constitute your acknowledgment of the modifications and your consent to abide and be bound by the modified privacy policy.</p>
            <p>If School Man makes any material changes to this privacy policy, School Man will notify you either through the email address you have provided to School Man, or by placing a prominent notice on the website.</p>

